# CPD Agenda Pipeline ŌĆö run context (.claude-md)

This file is the reference context for the CPD Agenda Processing
Pipeline. The Cowork scheduled task reads it at the start of every run.

The Cowork session finalises this file AFTER deployment (filling in the
web app URL, shared secret and folder IDs from Claude Code's report)
and places it at `/CPD-Inbox/.claude-md`.

Treat the web app URL and shared secret as secrets. This file lives
only in the `/CPD-Inbox/` Drive folder ŌĆö never commit it to a repo.

